annotations: Canadian steel - ingot production totaled 291,890 metric tons in the week ended Oct. 7 , up 14.8 % from the preceding week 's total of 254,280 tons , Statistics Canada , a federal agency , said .
The week 's total was up 6.2 % from 274,963 tons a year earlier .
The year - to - date total was 12,006,883 tons , up 7.8 % from 11,141,711 tons a year earlier .
